	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Go to Jaheira's House with Jaheira&#xD;&#xA;- Talk to Jaheira's Eldest Daughter inside the house, while staying in earshot&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Bookmark: larian://bookmark?name=CTY_JaheirasHouse&amp;mod=GustavDev&amp;level=CTY_Main_A&amp;camPos=-198.180267;36.128036;-47.551403&amp;camTarget=-198.939575;35.720970;-47.043709" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="365" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Conversation with Jaheira's Daughter if your party has Jaheira in and your player is not nearby. Mainly backstory and context for Jaheira and her daughter. It would be great to touch on why Jaheira''s nervous to leave Baldur's Gate without her influence to help build into the Timeless Body scroll story.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Currently is nearly identical to LOW_JaheiraAndDaughter01_OM_Jaheira_COM to try and capture the same beats, but absolutely can be different." />
